4:
She's strong, beautiful, and her
fashion is SO on point. Literally, a
trend-setter.
6:
Everyone LOVES her. Like, there are
so many girls that went into
adventuring because of her.
8:
Levy Grace deserves the world! Go
get it, queen!
11:
My name is Levy Grace. You've
probably heard a lot about me
being perfection personified.
14:
But that's all lies. The truth is, I'm just
out here faking it and giving the
people what they want. My combat
ability is middling at best.
18:
But I DO know how to dream. And
my dream is to be a master
adventurer! I want to conquer the
depths and gone where no one has
gone before!
23:
I don't know what to do... Give up on
training and be this glamorous diva
who never breaks a nail? Or follow
my dreams and leave my fans
behind?
30:
All right, all right! No pushing! We've
got plenty of these autographed
copies of Levy Grace's new book!
32:
O-oh my gosh... Levy, queeen. I've
been your fan for, like, the longest
time!
38:
Thank you. I hope this book is
everything you wished for and more.
43:
Way to go, Levy! "How to Farm
Haniwa and Get Rich Fast" is flying
off the shelves! That second printing
is in the bag!
46:
Um... So about my schedule... I was
wondering if I maybe had time to go
adventuring?
49:
Are you kidding me?! We've gotta
work while the hype around your
book is HOT! I'm thinking interviews
and modeling gigs.
50:
Man, I'm so busy booking
appointments, I haven't showered in
days!
54:
Yeah... Yeah, I know. But do you think
I could at least go home and sleep
today? Pick up where we left off
tomorrow?
57:
Affirmative. We need to keep that
skin fresh and glowing! Go get your
beauty sleep, queen!
61:
Ugh, I have, like, no stamina! Is it my
diet? No, it's definitely my muscles...
Gotta find out a way to work out in
secret.
65:
*sigh* How did things even come to
this?
68:
It started off with just, "oh, wow. I can
run the shallows super fast." And
then I wrote a book to help girls
realize adventuring ISN'T a man's
game. And now, I'm some kind of
idol?
70:
I JUST started exploring the
midways. Really, nothing to make a
big deal over.
76:
That's a large crowd. You are very
popular Alk.
81:
It's not called "popular" when they're
all trying to end you!
90:
Shift gears! I've got this side of the
room!
101:
You're not hurt, right? Next time,
when you're running from monsters,
find a place to hide. Otherwise,
you're gonna build up a giant mob
again.
104:
Thanks for the advice. Uh, by the
way, I'm Alk and...
112:
Levy. Levy Grace! I'm guessing
you've heard of me.
117:
Oh yeeeah! I've read one of your
books. What was it? How to beat a
thing 365 times or something?
121: "365 Ways to Defeat a Giant Spider."
126: That's it! It was, uh, interesting.
134:
Hey, would you guys like to take, like
an... adventuring seminar?
137:
Levy Grace gives you tips and tricks
on being an adventurer! That kind of
thing.

...Sound lame?
145:
Well, if Stella's curious... Is there any
kind of fee to join?
148:
What? Of course not. You guys
helped me come up with the idea. I
should be paying YOU.
153:
Well, I never turn down a paycheck!
A fat wallet means fancy meals.
157:
(I'm a GENIUS! This way, I can tell my
manager I'm hanging out with fans
and doing PR, but what I'll ACTUALLY
be doing is training and
adventuring!)
160:
Oh. But just to let you know, we, uh...
tend to travel pretty far. Is that cool
with you?
163: Yeah, for sure. I'll go anywhere.
166:
Well, guys, I hope you're ready.
'Cause we are in for an exhilarating
ride!
